+name: myWorkflow
+
+on:

+    branches: [ master ]
+

+
+jobs:
+
+  test:

+    steps:

+    runs-on: ubuntu-latest
+
+    steps:
+      - uses: actions/checkout@v2
+      - name: Build with Gradle
+        run: ./gradlew build
